headline: MARK & GRAHAM EXPANDS SANDERSON COLLABORATION
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, February 10, 2026--Mark & Graham, a portfolio brand of Williams-Sonoma, Inc. (NYSE: WSM), the world’s largest digital-first, design-led and sustainable home retailer, announced the next chapter of its collaboration with iconic English design house, Sanderson. Following the debut of Sanderson for Mark & Graham last February, the popular collaboration now includes bath products available for personalization that reimagine Sanderson’s timeless English patterns as elevated essentials

headline: Evercore ISI Group Maintains In-Line on Williams-Sonoma, Raises Price Target to $215
summary: Evercore ISI Group  analyst Oliver Wintermantel   maintains Williams-Sonoma (NYSE:WSM) with a In-Line and raises the price target from $210 to $215.
